the meeting was mainly about the exchange of the preliminary ideas about a new tv remote control project and subsequent task assignment .
the project manager first set a target of making a fifty million euros ' profit from the project , with the unit price of twenty-five euros .
afterwards , the team raised different opinions about features of the new remote controls and related questions about market potential .
among all the features , having a good look and size was unanimously considered to be the most essential .
in the end , marketing was assigned to investigate market competition and design , and user interface thinking about shapes , colours and other attributes which would attract customers .
